        "source": "Traveler (Geo)",
        "description": "A4 Frenzied Rockslide: the final hit of a Normal Attack combo triggers a collapse, dealing 60% ATK as AoE Geo DMG. The evaluator has no hit-specific flat-ATK-ratio key (normal_dmgIncFromAtk_ applies uniformly to every Normal Attack hit in the combo, not just the last), so this is approximated by spreading the 60% ATK bonus evenly across all 5 Normal Attack hits (0.60 / 5 = 0.12 ATK-ratio per hit); accurate for full 5-hit combo rotations, will misestimate for partial combos.",
